<p><font>PROTOZOIC</font><font> =
        "containing the earliest traces of living beings</font>."
        Hence the lustreless eye stares from the dawn of living
        time, in continuance of the evolutionist version of
        contemporary anti-Semitism. The slime of the Nile was
        long thought to contain the seeds of all animal and
        vegetable life, especially in Egypt, and presumably
        Bleistein has an overview of Jewish persecution from the
        exodus to present day Venice.</p>
